  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate clinical result including plaque index, gingival
      inflammation, bleeding score, pocket depth reduction and clinical attachment level gain after
      used locally-delivered gel containing Camella sinensis extracts as an adjunctive treatment in
      periodontal therapy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
