  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  subjects have sound tooth with pocket depth = or &gt; 5 mm. without caries, restoration,
             mobility and furcation involvement

          -  no systemic complicated factors

          -  no allergy to green tea or product of green tea

          -  signing in informed consent form

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  smoking

          -  pregnancy or lactation

          -  antibiotic premedication or antibiotic intake in previous 3 month
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
